'''Rudyard Kipling''', né à [[Bombay]], alors en [[Inde|Inde britannique]], l' 30 ed décimbe 1865 et mort à [[Londe]], l' 18 ed jinvier 1936, ch'est un écrivin [[Roéyôme-Uni|britannike]].

{|
|[[Image:Illustration at Cover of Just So Stories (c1912).jpg|thumb|upright=0.8| ''Just So Stories'' (c1912)]]
|[[Image:Jungle Book Rudyard Kipling poster.jpeg|thumb|upright=0.9|right|Afike pour ch' ''Live éd la jungle'' (vers 1900)]]
|}





<poem>
:Take up the White Man's burden—
:Send forth the best ye breed—
:Go, bind your sons to exile
:To serve your captives' need;
:To wait, in heavy harness,
:On fluttered folk and wild—
:Your new-caught sullen peoples,
:Half devil and half child</poem>



